## 🔧 Breaking Changes

- **`multi_validator_consensus_enabled` default changed from `False` → `True`** — `MultiValidatorPoA`/`PBFTConsensus` now instantiate on demand. Single-validator PoA still produces blocks. Set `MULTI_VALIDATOR_CONSENSUS_ENABLED=false` in env to re-disable.
- **`escrow_enabled` default changed from `False` → `True`** — settlement RPC endpoints and `CrossChainSettlementService` now active. Set `ESCROW_ENABLED=false` in env to re-disable.
- The `simple_exchange_api.py` shim is retained for backward compatibility but is no longer used by any launcher.

