### `apps/blockchain-node/src/aitbc_chain/`
- `database.py` — `_migrate_existing_columns()`, `class_=Session` on sessionmakers, `init_db()` calls migration
- `rpc/accounts.py` — 6 `session_scope()` calls fixed to pass `chain_id`
- `rpc/router.py` — 10 settlement routes pass `settings.chain_id` to `CrossChainSettlementService`; dispute/resolve routes pass `settings.chain_id` + `session.commit()`
