- `sync.py` — removed changed-addresses tracking + `account_map` building; always full recompute
- `sync_cli.py` — added `init_db(settings.chain_id)` before `ChainSync` start
- `app.py` — added `init_cross_chain_bridge(session_scope)` call in lifespan startup
- `config.py` — `multi_validator_consensus_enabled: True`, `escrow_enabled: True` (enabled for homebrew testing, no external security audit)

