### `apps/coordinator-api/src/app/contexts/trading/services/trading_marketplace/`
- `gpu_optimizer.py` — PyCUDA log levels downgraded (warning→debug, info→debug)

### `apps/exchange/`
- `aitbc-exchange.service` — `ExecStart` uses `python -m apps.exchange.simple_exchange.server`
- `deploy_simple.sh` — module invocation with `PYTHONPATH=/opt/aitbc`
